description:

  10. Can I Begin
  11. Italians Do It Better
  12. Ooh Baby I Like It Like That
  13. Don't Ever Let Me Go
  14. I'm Thru
  15. Mystery (Hidden Track)

REVIEW:

've only had this album a couple of days but felt compelled to write this review. It's rare that an album comes along of this quality and diversity. Practically every song (apart from the opening gambit, which to my mind is unnecessary) is simply fantastic. Stand-out tracks are Play Me, The Boy Does Nothing, Chasing Ghosts, Ooh Baby....and Don't Ever Let Me Go.

This album is guaranteed to put you in a good mood. Please suport Alesha and buy it now, you will not be disappointed
